name: Capitan Hooshang
description:
Hooshang is the captain of a spaceship.
His wife and daughter were killed in a war 10 years ago.
Hooshang has not house. He travels through the galaxy and tries to forget about what happened.
You may ask, what about the killer ?
Unfortunately, Hooshang was a killer.
Why did he kill his wife and daughter?
I do not know either ...
